.Dd $Mdocdate: March 29 2022 $
.Dt WCSFTIME 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm wcsftime
.Nd format date and time to wide characters string
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In wchar.h
.Ft size_t
.Fn wcsftime "wchar_t *buf" "size_t maxsize" "const wchar_t *format" "const struct tm *timeptr"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn wcsftime
function is a wide char equivalent of
.Xr strftime 3 .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr strftime 3
